node.text: We just had an 80lb blacktip shark bust our terminal tackle. Can you name another species of fish that weighs 80lbs that can destroy terminal tackle like this with around 10lbs of drag? #blacktiph #fishing #terminaltackle #tackle #busted #hook #rig #blacktip #blacktipshark #surffishing

node.text: In this video, I go fishing with Florida Fish and Wildlife Conservation Commission on Lake Weohyakapka using electricity to catch giant fish! Our goal was to find a 10lb bass. We caught a monster 10lb and 12lb bass!!

node.title: Using ELECTRICITY to Catch GIANT Fish

node.text: Most fishermen dream of catching a world record-sized fish, especially a world record tarpon! We caught this massive Tarpon in Colombia with @fishcolombia and @docb22 in Bahía Solano. We had no idea how big this fish truly was until we got on some WIFI at the lodge and started doing some research. After speaking with @delphfishing and Raymond Douglas from @kingsailfishmounts and using the @bonefishtarpontrust tarpon weight calculator, we estimated that our fish was around 312lbs, beating the current world record by over 25lbs! We used a goggle eye for bait. Colombia has massive tarpon and if you want to catch one over 200lbs, I highly recommend booking a trip with @fishcolombia #blacktiph #fishing #tarpon #record #worldrecord #tarponfishing #colombia #pacific #ocean #fish #monsterfish 📷 @davis_bennett_

node.text: Had an absolute blast in Alabama with @fishalabama and @captain_kurt_t! Caught some huge scamp groupers, yellowedge groupers and some jumbo red snappers! The bottom fishing off Gulf Shores is incredible and I highly recommend planning a fishing trip here and bringing the family! Lots of fun things to do in Gulf Shores, Alabama! #blacktiph #fishing #alabama #alabamafishing #fishalabama #scamp #yellowedgegrouper #deepsea #grouper 📸 @davis_bennett_

node.text: Throwback to the most epic topwater redfish bite I’ve ever seen! Filmed with @finao_sportfishing and @stephenson_h5 in Virginia #blacktiph #fishing #topwater #redfish #drum #reddrum #topwater #topwaterfishing #virginia #ocean 📸 @davis_bennett_

node.accessibility_caption: Photo by BlacktipH in Oregon Inlet with @davis_bennett_, @nc_travis, @joshua_jorgensen, @blacktiphbrand, and @afishionadocharters. May be an image of 1 person.

node.text: Caught the biggest tuna of my life with @afishionadocharters. We saw monster bluefin tuna airing out for hours, it was absolutely incredible! This tuna was so big, we struggled to fit it in the frame! Huge shoutout to @nc_travis for all the help! #blacktiph #fishing #tuna #bluefin #bluefintuna #tunafishing #northcarolina #outerbanks #oregoninlet #fish #ocean 📸 @davis_bennett_
